data.description: Enjoy maintenance free living while situated on a .25+ acre corner cul-de-sac lot with a preserve view in Villages of Thousand Oaks! Inside you will find a tastefully updated kitchen with granite countertops, wood cabinets, eat-in kitchen space, breakfast bar, and stainless-steel appliances. The living room boasts wood flooring, updated can lighting, and a sliding glass door with direct access to your enclosed lanai! The enclosed lanai opens to a spacious outdoor paver patio and the .25+ acre yard perfect for entertaining guests, grilling out, or relaxing while you listen to the wildlife all around you! Directly off the living room is the owner’s suite which offers a large built-in closet, and an ensuite bathroom with a walk-in shower! Villages of Thousand Oaks features a heated pool, tennis courts, and beautiful grounds full of mature trees and exceptional landscaping. While having a low HOA and No CDDs the community provides full maintenance of the grounds so you know your yard will stay beautiful year-round! For weekend outings, you'll have tons of options including the Ellenton Premium Outlets, Starbucks, Publix, Ellenton Ice and Sports Complex, and restaurants galore! Not to mention you are in the middle of the new North River district with a multitude of new upcoming shopping, dining, and activities! Is this your perfect match? Schedule your private showing today!
